#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:16
msgid "Project and Asset Management"
msgstr "Beheer van project en bezittingen"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:32
msgid ""
"Kdenlive works with projects. A project contains all the :term:"
"`assets<Asset>` (sources), the :term:`timeline` with your :term:"
"`clips<Clip>` in different :term:`tracks<Track>`, the cuts and trims, :term:"
"`compositions<Composition>` and :term:`transitions<Transition>`, :doc:"
"`annotations</project_and_asset_management/project_notes>`, :term:"
"`markers`, :term:`guides<Guide>` - in short, everything you and Kdenlive "
"need to produce a video file as the result of your work."
msgstr ""
"Kdenlive werkt met projecten. Een project bevat alle :term:"
"`bezittingen<Asset>` (bronnen), de :term:`tijdlijn` met uw :term:"
"`clips<Clip>` in verschillende :term:`tracks<Track>`, de afsnijdingen en "
"trims, :term:`composities<Composition>` en :term:`overgangen<Transition>`, :"
"doc:`annotaties</project_and_asset_management/project_notes>`, :term:"
"`markeringen`, :term:`hulplijnen<Guide>` - in het kort, alles wat u en "
"Kdenlive nodig hebben om een videobestand te produceren als het resultaat "
"van uw werk."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:35
msgid ""
"When creating a project, select a project profile with the final video in "
"mind. The :doc:`project settings</project_and_asset_management/"
"project_settings>` determine the resolution (e.g. 1920x1080), the frame rate "
"(e.g. 25 fps), other :doc:`meta data</project_and_asset_management/"
"project_settings/tab_meta_data>`, and how to deal with the project's assets."
msgstr ""
"Bij aanmaken van een project, selecteer een projectprofiel met de "
"uiteindelijke video in gedachte. De :doc:`projectinstellingen</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_settings>` bepalen de resolutie (bijv. "
"1920x1080), de framesnelheid (bijv. 25 fps), andere :doc:`metagegevens</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_settings/tab_meta_data>` en hoe om te "
"gaan met de bezittingen van het project."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:38
msgid ""
"You can change the project profile later but it is not recommended as it may "
"lead to undesirable results, in particular when you use keyframes."
msgstr ""
"U kunt het projectprofiel later wijzigen maar dat is niet aanbevolen omdat "
"het kan leiden tot ongewenste resultaten, speciaal wanneer u keyframes "
"gebruikt."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:40
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Project Bin</project_and_asset_management/project_bin>` holds all "
"your assets. You can load (or import) video and audio files, single images "
"or entire :doc:`image sequences</project_and_asset_management/project_bin/"
"image_sequence>`, create :doc:`color</project_and_asset_management/"
"project_bin/color_clip>` and :doc:`title clips</titles_and_graphics/titles/"
"titles>`, :doc:`animations</titles_and_graphics/graphics_and_animations/"
"glaxnimate>`, and download assets from various :doc:`online sources</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_bin/online_resources>` directly into "
"your project."
msgstr ""
"De :doc:`Project-bin</project_and_asset_management/project_bin>` houd al uw "
"bezittingen. U kunt video- en audiobestanden laden (of importeren), enkele "
"afbeeldingen of gehele :doc:`afbeeldingsreeksen</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_bin/image_sequence>`, :doc:`kleur</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_bin/color_clip>` en :doc:`titelclips</"
"titles_and_graphics/titles/titles>`, :doc:`animaties</titles_and_graphics/"
"graphics_and_animations/glaxnimate>` en bezittingen downloaden uit "
"verschillende :doc:`online bronnen</project_and_asset_management/project_bin/"
"online_resources>` direct in uw project."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:42
msgid ""
"While the project bin is for a specific project, you can use the :doc:"
"`library</project_and_asset_management/library>` feature to store assets for "
"use in other projects. That is also the only way to share or copy assets "
"between projects."
msgstr ""
"Terwijl de project-bin er is voor een specifiek project, kunt u de functie :"
"doc:`bibliotheek</project_and_asset_management/library>` gebruiken om "
"bezittingen voor gebruik in andere projecten opslaan. Dat is ook de enige "
"manier om bezittingen te delen of bezittingen te kopiëren tussen projecten."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:44
msgid ""
"Kdenlive offers limited :doc:`video</project_and_asset_management/"
"capturing_video>` and :doc:`audio</project_and_asset_management/"
"capturing_audio>` capturing functionality, for example to create voice "
"overs, or use screenshots."
msgstr ""
"Kdenlive biedt beperkte functies voor :doc:`video</"
"project_and_asset_management/capturing_video>` en :doc:`audio</"
"project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio>` opnemen, om bijvoorbeeld "
"voice-overs of schermafdrukken te gebruiken."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:46
msgid ""
"You can :doc:`take notes</project_and_asset_management/project_notes>` for "
"your project that capture timestamps for easy reference during the editing "
"process. This is very useful for big and complex projects or productions."
msgstr ""
"U kunt :doc:`notities maken</project_and_asset_management/project_notes>` "
"voor uw project die tijdstippen opneemt voor gemakkelijke verwijzing "
"gedurende het bewerkingsproces. Dat is erg nuttig voor grote en complexe "
"projecten of producties."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management.rst:48
msgid ""
"Kdenlive has an :doc:`auto-save feature</project_and_asset_management/"
"file_management/auto_save>`, creates :doc:`backups</"
"project_and_asset_management/file_management/backup>` in the background, and "
"allows to :doc:`archive a project</project_and_asset_management/"
"file_management/archiving>` with all the assets included."
msgstr ""
"Kdenlive heeft een :doc:`automatisch opslaan mogelijkheid</"
"project_and_asset_management/file_management/auto_save>`, maakt :doc:"
"`reservekopieën</project_and_asset_management/file_management/backup>` op de "
"achtergrond en biedt het :doc:`een project archiveren</"
"project_and_asset_management/file_management/archiving>` met alle "
"bezittingen meegenomen."
